spec_data.Name: texlive-censor
spec_data.Description:
The package allows a convenient redaction/censor capability to
be employed, for those who need to protect restricted
information, etc. The package can "redact" anything that can be
enclosed by a LaTeX box.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:22:16 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Facilities for controlling restricted text in a document
